  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical heart failure

          -  Preserved ejection fraction (&gt;50%)

          -  Stable clinically

          -  New York Heart Association Class II-III

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Unable to exercise

          -  Other debilitating or unstable disease limiting length of life

          -  Implanted pacemaker
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
